      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1988 Porsche 911 Carrera 3.2, featuring the highly desirable G50 Getrag five-speed transaxle with Borg-Warner synchronizers. This air-cooled flat-six remains in factory-spec configuration, utilizing Bosch Motronic DME engine management for optimal fuel mapping and throttle response. The chassis exhibits zero structural fatigue, retaining its original torsion bar suspension geometry and staggered Fuchs forged alloy wheels. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the top end is dry with no evidence of oil migration, and the synchros provide crisp, positive engagement. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically superlative example with original paint depth and pristine undercarriage integrity.",
